snippet.title: Chris Evans as Buzz Lightyear; Ant-Man 3; Amber Heard in House of Ashes? Pokémon Cereal
snippet.description: Pandora's expansion at Animal Kingdom confirmed for WDW; Chris Evans to replace Tim Allen in Toy Story 5 as Buzz Lightyear; Amber Heard rumored to be in House of Hell aka House of Ashes, in stores April 2021; The Nun 2; Ant-Man 3; Ant-Man and Wasp ride at Magic Kingdom of WDW; Pokemon cereal; Ellen hiatusing her show until January 2021 due to her diagnosis of CV; Abomination returns in She-Hulk on Disney+; two LA Disney movie teasers launched.
